column3: “I have 2 compression fractures in my back. I tried to take the muscle relaxers and narcotics I was prescribed, but as soon as I got this stuff it was completely non needed. this makes my pain drift away.. I've never experienced a daytime high" until smoking this. rather than making me energetic and motivated
column4: I feel like it energizes my mind which takes me far away from wherever I am and makes me thing deeply about ...”"

“This Kind of strain is Amazing, starting from the bud, arriving to be really stoned It gives you Energy and let you feel less heavy! 

From an italian living in Jamaica!”
“Just pulled my Mama after 4 months.  Shout out to Puamana Seed Bank!  This one is killah!”

“Pretty damn good strain. From the first exhale, you immediately will taste the tropical notes of mango just like a smoothie. I absolutely love the taste of this strain, and man is it fruity. If you ever get the chance to consume this amazing herb, realize its awesomeness. You will notice that the high is very very clear headed. There seems to be a low to minimal haze hat you would get usually. I found that this strai...”
“For this to be a sativa dominant hybrid, it sure does hit like an indica. The diesel and the sweet fruity taste is a great combination!!”
“Taste fruity. Real good high while being productive. Two thumbs up! Mahalo! Pakalolo brah!”
“A great diesel that has a sweet flavour and aroma to it. The pull is real smooth and high that is quite euphoric.”
“This strain reflects the name in perfect harmony, mango, diesel and the unique tropical maui wowie heritage are all present and welcomed hit after hit.”

“The smell of this bud just hits you like a fresh mango to the face. The taste is once again a strong tropical and sweet one with mango being the main bit. This is a good daytime high, I felt immediately relaxed but not tired. This strain made me a little hungry and lightly thirsty. The look of the bud was a nice green with some darker leaves dotting the fluffy nuggs. As for the Keef this strain wasn’t particularly ca...”

Maui Mango Diesel

You will rarely find a strain more exotic and ʻono (delicious) than our Pua Mana 1st Hawaiian Pakalōlō Seed Bankʻs genetic masterpiece Maui Mango Diesel!

The mother plant is our finest Brooklyn Mango from Dr. Underground.
We crossed her with our most powerful Kāne (male) Maui Wowie to create our most ...”
“got this stuff in amsterdam was just called mango diesel tho it was one of the best strains ive ever smoke good high but the flavour is the best but really sweet and fruity amazing”

“Definitely up there with tangerine dream as far a tasting incredible. Fresh mangos! The high is incredibly relaxing but clearheaded. I use it as a day strain and there’s no “dopeyness” to it. Feels great, makes me smile, and removes any tension  good for relieving my tension headaches and causes no anxiety for me (thankfully). 
P.S. If you are prone to auditory hallucinations like I am, this has never caused me any. ...”
“I'm not a big fan of Sativa dominate hybrids but if you need to get things done I would recommend”
